  "doc_id": "60786",
  "text": "However, AqpZ containing nanodiscs consistently showed a significant depletion of CL (to 6.2 ± 2.1 % wt/wt) at the expence of PE. This observation was independent of the mutant protein examined, since little variation in lipid head-group composition was observed between nanodiscs containing the C 20 S protein and those containing the W 14 A protein. Our observation contrasts with previous studies on SMA nanodiscs containing KcsA [CITATION_1] and Sec [CITATION_2] in which a CL enrichment was observed. This indicates that the observed lipid composition of SMA nanodiscs depends on the protein they contain.",
